				<p>
					<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="subaudible"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> pukaḻmātu viḷaṅka <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yamātu virumpa nilamakaḷ nilava malarmakaḷ puṇara Urimaiyiṟ ci
					<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟan=ta maṇimuṭi cūṭi minavar nilaikeṭa vi<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied>lavar kulaitara En<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>mannava ririyaluṟ ṟaḻitara tikkanaittuñ cakkara naṭā<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>ti vīra<hi rend="grantha">siṁ</hi><unclear>ñā</unclear><hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>na<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>tu A
					<lb n="3" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> ṭu vīṟṟirun=taruḷiya ko<hi rend="grantha">rāja</hi>kecaripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>rāna <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vanaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇ
					<lb n="4" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> koṇṭacoḻavaḷanāṭṭut tirumunaippāṭik kiḻānmūrnāṭṭu Āti<hi rend="grantha">rāja</hi>maṅkaliyapurattu U<unclear>ṭaiyār</unclear>
					<lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> nittavinotavaḷanāṭṭu Āvūṟkūṟṟattu kiḷiyūruṭaiyān veḷā naṅkāṭiyāna keraḷa<hi rend="grantha">rāja</hi>n vaitta tirunantā
					<lb n="6" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> ṭa cāvā muvā perāṭu <num value="96">9 <g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num> <supplied reason="subaudible"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Ivvāṭu toṇṇūṟṟāṟuṅ kaikkoṇṭu tirunantāviḷak kerikkakaṭa
					<lb n="7" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> koyilil tiruvuḷ<unclear>nā</unclear>ḻikai<hi rend="grantha">sahai</hi>yom <supplied reason="subaudible"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmahā</hi>ye<hi rend="grantha">śvara rakṣai</hi> <supplied reason="subaudible"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> 
